---
title: Creamy Chicken and Mushroom Alfredo with Linguine and Spinach
description: Perfect pasta doesn't take a lot of ingredients or time! This creamy chicken Alfredo has a secret ingredient: soy sauce! Adding soy sauce to the mushrooms gives this Alfredo an umami kick.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/linguines-alfredo-cremeuses-au-poulet-et-aux-champignons-cc7b56f7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/creamy-chicken-and-mushroom-alfredo-658a27714bc4c8bdd3072d8a-8d7dbc3d.pdf
